    "We will now describe how to perform the U SP and U CSP circuits.|0 m ⟩ U SP |ψ⟩ |0 n-m ⟩ U CSP SP Circuit StructureTo perform U SP, we give a method that has depth O(m) and uses O(2 m) ancilla qubits.",
